test with the latest commit. 

Current known issues : Ghost pieces.
                       Occasional lock up in cases where 2 white pawns are next to each other in the same row. 
                       Being able to select pieces that cannot move. 
                       Being able to select and move ghost pieces. 
                       
                       Objective of the game : 1 player : get all the pieces to the other side
                                                          This is possible
                       
                                               2 player : get all 3 of your pieces to the other side first
                                               Tie condition is possible
                                               both win conditions are possible
                                                                
                                                                
